section.section:
Subject to subsection (c) of this section, an invitation for auction bids shall include:
the specifications of the procurement contract;
whether the procurement contract will be awarded based on the lowest bid price or the lowest evaluated bid price;
if the procurement contract will be based on evaluated bid price, the objective measurable criteria by which the lowest evaluated bid price will be determined;
the small business preference, if designated under § 13-103 of this subtitle; and
the date and time when bidding will commence and the date and time when bidding will end or the event upon which bidding will end.
